What was that about?

09:10.466 --> 09:11.600
What was...

09:12.677 --> 09:13.811
I don't...

09:14.095 --> 09:15.239
It was about...

09:15.263 --> 09:17.273
Being close to
you, I don't know.

09:17.557 --> 09:18.899
It's been a while.

09:20.643 --> 09:22.278
I just miss kissing you.

09:27.358 --> 09:28.742
Okay, uh...

09:29.318 --> 09:31.996
I've got stuff I
need to bring down.

09:34.323 --> 09:35.884
<i>But when they checked
under their bed</i>

09:35.908 --> 09:37.960
<i>to make sure they'd
packed everything,</i>

09:37.994 --> 09:40.045
<i>they found something strange.</i>

09:40.162 --> 09:42.099
<i>There, behind the missing socks,</i>

09:42.123 --> 09:44.383
<i>a thick, ugly weed was growing.</i>

09:44.667 --> 09:46.061
<i>And they knew from its size</i>

09:46.085 --> 09:48.262
<i>that it must have
been there a while.</i>

09:49.338 --> 09:51.432
Okay, okay, that's true, but...

09:52.091 --> 09:53.360
He did have three desserts,

09:53.384 --> 09:55.644
and he was writing
the whole time.

09:55.886 --> 09:58.480
He hardly touched
the tuna tartar.

09:58.556 --> 10:00.617
I knew the cilantro
was a mistake.

10:00.641 --> 10:01.827
How could he finish
all those dishes?

10:01.851 --> 10:03.161
I mean, he ordered
half the menu.

10:03.185 --> 10:04.288
Well, he had to.

10:04.312 --> 10:07.323
With Jason clearing the
plates every five seconds.

10:07.565 --> 10:08.699
Well,

10:08.733 --> 10:10.284
I thought we did pretty well.

10:10.985 --> 10:11.878
I did.

10:11.902 --> 10:14.121
I mean, except for the
tuna, didn't you?

10:15.531 --> 10:16.665
Hello?

10:17.825 --> 10:18.959
Claudia?

10:19.577 --> 10:20.846
Now? I forgot... I
forgot all about it.

10:20.870 --> 10:22.004
What channel is it?

10:22.580 --> 10:24.131
Okay, bye.

10:25.833 --> 10:27.519
<i>...and, of course my entire...</i>

10:27.543 --> 10:30.897
Oh, my God, she won.
Charlie, she won.

10:30.921 --> 10:32.181
<i>Success like this...</i>

10:33.633 --> 10:35.559
<i>God, this thing is heavy.</i>

10:36.427 --> 10:38.103
<i>You don't get this on your own.</i>

10:38.888 --> 10:42.191
<i>You need people who are
willing to back you up</i>

10:42.683 --> 10:47.873
<i>and give you the room to learn and...
And to make mistakes.</i>

10:47.897 --> 10:49.082
<i>So,</i>

10:49.106 --> 10:51.867
<i>uh, well, Charlie,</i>

10:52.234 --> 10:53.619
<i>I love you.</i>

11:10.294 --> 11:11.438
<i>Hi, leave a message</i>

11:11.462 --> 11:14.223
<i>and some Salinger or another
will get back to you. Promise.</i>

