<i>Hi, this is Dr.
Reichman's office.</i>

11:16.300 --> 11:19.978
<i>Just a reminder, Claudia has a checkup
and a cleaning tomorrow at 4:00.</i>

11:22.223 --> 11:23.524
<i> Hi, um,</i>

11:24.225 --> 11:26.193
<i>I'm trying to reach Jake Gordon.</i>

11:26.685 --> 11:28.580
<i>Maybe this isn't
